Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是統轄部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第707補給基地，請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第707補給基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是聯合統轄部，能聽到嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也無法變回人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想最後見你一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是綾人君？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心率上升，到達活動臨界點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-3向莉麗亞·立特巴克報告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上空的RahXephon放射出gamma射線…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲司令讓我保管的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貳神君…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我不叫那個名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你利用M型標本第一號製造出來的…你的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名教授
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-1，緊急降落至B甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪亞特中尉準備使用殘存的戰鬥機再次出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令，中尉請求許可使用TDD裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果，等著我的只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達到yolteotl階段的你的真實形態嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dnepr號、Scharnhorst號被擊沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.36,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dnepr：第聶伯河，歐洲第四大河，全長981公里，流經全烏克蘭，南入黑海\NScharnhorst：沙恩霍地斯特號，二戰時期的德國海軍戰列巡洋艦\N滿載排水量3.9萬噸，艦長230米，航速32節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pernemunde號停止運行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.54,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pernemunde研究所，二戰中德國開發出v1、v2飛彈的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄！一邊後退一邊攻擊！決不妥協！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，本艦向敵軍的中心前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變航向右轉舵6點(67.5度)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉，我想賭一賭你的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，TDD可以用作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不要同歸於盡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到它面前就立刻釋放，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我說「不」呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許你出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，八雲司令，我還沒有那麼愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧，夥計！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha 1，起飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6點方向有D-1！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿刺場，諧振開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場發生器最大功率輸出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射偏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別耍小聰明了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊…神的心臟啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死浩子的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…我不會接受的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種人…你這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種殺死浩子的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間已到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界被聲音充滿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調律的時刻現在就要來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，怎麼了？為什麼你這麼痛苦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙，不能再待在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別耍小孩子脾氣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總一！一定要回來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生…我已經盡力而為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…結果就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:09:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…不行了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金…和你的約定無法兌現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總一！ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…是我幹的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是我幹的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，這些就是你做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此你還要繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此你還會繼續活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了現在，我的樂團指揮的職責也結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺住！快到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個一切都即將改變的世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為人類繼續活下去，究竟還有多少意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，每一個倖存下來的人都有他應該去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點是很清楚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類即使遭遇到這種事情也還是會繼續生存下去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退命令已經下達…雖然命令上是這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看起來無論逃到哪裡都是一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有必須去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骯髒的工作就由我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙我的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙視我的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我「D」的傢伙都得去死…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力按住！小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉麗亞·立特巴克沉沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾菲和八雲都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你和RahXephon一起消失了，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和RahXephon一起在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon在我體內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自身就是RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不再是一個人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你…因為你總一他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把總一還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不死之身，什麼瑪士撒拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.97,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}瑪士撒拉(methuselah)：《聖經·創世紀》中人物，據傳享年969歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打中了，還不是會死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是D
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D是designer's children的D，是Dolem的D
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許叫我D…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且D是表示殘次品的D
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！死吧！去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？為什麼總一都不放過？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要什麼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總一…把我的總一還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照自己的方式繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不再是人類了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是你！是人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經明白我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon的存在對於我有著什麼樣的意義…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ixtli in yolteotl
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去人類心臟的olin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到神的心臟——yolteotl\N接受「真實」的「容顏」——ixtli(伊修特利)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，和你互補的「另一個你」\N你的「另一半」有了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是將時間物質化，由機械裝置構成的神…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾多世界的流浪者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使世界安定、調和的調律者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的歌會使世界融為一體…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要恐懼，我的「另一半」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一切都是你的，你的一切都和我在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好活下去，olin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，請和綾人一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導他，把我和你的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見她的歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠，和我有血緣關係的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是「另一個你」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的世界和我的世界，誰的世界會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興能生而為人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的心感受過各種各樣的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你也相知了兩次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙，我最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不能接受…辦不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你…是我唯一愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等待…這一時刻…這個結局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多麼地令人興奮和期待啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青色的森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:32.35,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}黑曜石之蝶：阿茲特克神話裡的女ltzpapalotl
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜石之蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重溫舊夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打破心的牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏真實的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙和久遠的過去與未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界飽含著聲音